name: Beldum
Attack1Text: Search your deck for a Basic Pokémon and put it onto your Bench. Shuffle your deck afterward.
Attack2Text: Put 1 damage counter on the Defending Pokémon.

name: Electrike
Attack1Text: Search your deck for a Lightning Energy card and attach it to Electrike. Shuffle your deck afterward.
Attack2Text: Flip a coin. If heads, this attack does 10 damage plus 20 more damage.

name: Grumpig
Attack1Text: Choose 1 of your opponent's Pokémon. This attack does 10 damage to that Pokémon. (Don't apply Weakness and Resistance for Benched Pokémon.)

name: Metang
Attack1Text: Does 10 damage plus 10 more damage for each Energy attached to the Defending Pokémon.
Attack2Text: Flip a coin. If heads, this attack does 40 damage plus 20 more damage.

name: Plusle
Attack1Text: Search your discard pile for an Energy card, show it to your opponent, and put it in your hand
Attack2Text: Does 20 damage to 1 of your opponent's Benched Pokémon. (Don't apply Weakness and Resistance for Benched Pokémon.)

name: Spoink
Attack1Text: Flip a coin. If heads, this attack does 10 damage plus 10 more damage.
